==English==

===Adjective===
'''fluorescent'''

#Of or relating to [[fluorescence]]
#[[Exhibiting]] or produced by [[fluorescence]]
#:''The fluorescent plants [[shimmered]] in the darkness.''
# [[Emit]]ting visible [[light]] as a result of the excitation of [[phosphor]]s by [[ultraviolet]] [[photon]]s produced by the passage of an [[electrical current]] through an [[inert gas]] infused with [[mercury]].
#:''The quality of fluorescent lighting technology has improved dramatically in recent years.''
#Glowing as if with fluorescence; vivid 
#:''The fluorescent colors were bright and [[gaudy]].''

